Chapter 5: HAVING
Problem
Find customers with sales above 10,000.
Thinking
Step 1
Need sales total.
GROUP BY
Step 2
Need filtering after grouping.
HAVING
Solution:
SELECT CustomerID,
SUM(Amount)
FROM Sales
GROUP BY CustomerID
HAVING SUM(Amount)>10000;
