Chapter 13: Incremental Loading
Most Common ADF Question.
________________________________________
Problem
Source has:
10 million rows
Today only:
1000 rows changed
Should we read all rows?
No
________________________________________
Thinking
Need only changed records.
Use:
Watermark
Last loaded date:
2026-07-01
SQL:
SELECT *
FROM Orders
WHERE ModifiedDate >
'2026-07-01';
________________________________________
Interview Question
What is watermarking?
Answer:
Technique to load only new or changed records
based on last successful load time.
________________________________________
Chapter 14: Running Total
Problem
Calculate cumulative sales.
Data:
100
200
300
Need:
100
300
600
________________________________________
Thinking
Need previous rows.
Window Function.
Use:
SUM OVER()
________________________________________
Solution
SELECT Date,
Amount,
SUM(Amount)
OVER(
ORDER BY Date
) RunningTotal
FROM Sales;
